{"tid":1630394,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黃大仙樂富有手足冇衫換","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:04:08.000Z","uid":79704,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"66dc755b9b6caeef477d1ef341def5ff0a152672","tid":1630394,"uid":79704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:20:28.000Z","msg":"有手足冇衫換，要街坊落去掩護，救人呀！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5323ac7a93b1ae54b44069a7a44222454f08717","tid":1630394,"uid":79704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:20:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51c23896fc76d74c87a95b92e918ecb7a99b84a6","tid":1630394,"uid":79704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:20:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"429ee365c75d10e38323c061adc14f85048562b9","tid":1630394,"uid":79704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:21:00.000Z","msg":"救人呀，散唔到呀"},{"pid":"4e8eafdf073f18954c24c13c9777f7cb9639d441","tid":1630394,"uid":79704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:21:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9a2f5f2941bafda8d97d0861c5aeaf2106d0605","tid":1630394,"uid":79704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:21:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eeb63d5c5b7193b14e3b7050b7a8c765e19f65ba","tid":1630394,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:22:12.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"347cd875c03741e77bfbbe30dc329bae8cc9833f","tid":1630394,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:22:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815fc70b6ba3312a2f9559d351eda476cb2f7ac0","tid":1630394,"uid":280475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:22:50.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"a33008c2c51a9fb798a132a68b6f5f8c7e7379d4","tid":1630394,"uid":86403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:23:55.000Z","msg":"好多鋪頭關左...自己小心搵位換"},{"pid":"f426aee653a9df3faeb559fcd08a6b8bc9cba4d1","tid":1630394,"uid":79704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:25:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a3dd10855d759d3f2afcf95ff15a20dfd096f61","tid":1630394,"uid":79704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:25:40.000Z","msg":"救人呀，要街坊呀"},{"pid":"408c1ac0e25eddc